OL,3,CSNP in denial over growing mental
OL,4,Chealth crisis, says Sarwar
OL,6,FJohn Swinney and the SNP are "in
OL,7,Fdenial" over Scotland's "growing
OL,8,Fmental health crisis", the Scottish
OL,9,FLabour leader has said.
OL,11,FSpeaking on Sunday, Anas Sarwar said
OL,12,Fchildren and young people are "falling
OL,13,Fthrough the cracks" regarding support
OL,14,Ffor mental health, despite a rise in
OL,15,Fdemand.
OL,26,@nD@^OUoD@GO]oD@YOUpD@UO]tD@_OUuD@SO]
