OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777770201
OL,3,CSNP in denial over growing mental
OL,4,Chealth crisis, says Sarwar
OL,6,FUsing information supplied through a
OL,7,Ffreedom of information (FOI) request,
OL,8,FScottish Labour also said more than
OL,9,F700,000 calls were made to NHS24's
OL,10,Fmental health hub between 2021 and
OL,11,F2025, arguing that their party would
OL,12,Fprovide the support needed to quell
OL,13,Fthe problem.
OL,15,FIf it gets into power, Labour said it
OL,16,Fwill create an emergency mental health
OL,17,Fresponse service for specialist care
OL,18,Fwhile freeing up Police Scotland so
OL,19,Fthey can tackle crime over mental
OL,20,Fhealth crises.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
