CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777770201
OL,3,CSNP in denial over growing mental
OL,4,Chealth crisis, says Sarwar
OL,6,FScottish Labour also said it would
OL,7,Falso increase NHS funding for mental
OL,8,Fhealth services, as well as the number
OL,9,Fof professionals in the sector, and
OL,10,Fprovide a new system for children and
OL,11,Fyoungsters who have been referred to
OL,12,Fthe Children and Young People's Mental
OL,13,FHealth Services (CAMHS).
OL,15,FMr Sarwar said: "There is a growing
OL,16,Fmental health crisis taking hold in
OL,17,FScotland but John Swinney and the SNP
OL,18,Fare in denial.
OL,26,@wD@QOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777770201
OL,3,CSNP in denial over growing mental
OL,4,Chealth crisis, says Sarwar
OL,6,F"Demand for mental health support is
OL,7,Fon the rise, but there still isn't a
OL,8,Fspecialist emergency response service
OL,9,Ffor people suffering a crisis.
OL,11,F"After 20 years of SNP government,
OL,12,Fmental health services are struggling
OL,13,Fto cope, kids are falling through the
OL,14,Fcracks at CAMHS and police are still
OL,15,Fresponding to mental health
OL,16,Femergencies.
OL,18,F"A Scottish Labour government will end
OL,19,Fthe SNP's neglect of mental health
OL,20,Fservices and make sure struggling
OL,21,FScots get the help they need."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOUzD@AOU}D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
