OL,3,CSNP in denial over growing mental
OL,4,Chealth crisis, says Sarwar
OL,6,FHe added: "We will establish a new
OL,7,Femergency service for mental health,
OL,8,Fimprove services across the board and
OL,9,Fmake sure kids don't fall through the
OL,10,Fcracks at CAMHS.
OL,12,F"Next week is our chance to turn the
OL,13,Fpage on SNP failure, vote for better
OL,14,Fmental health services and deliver a
OL,15,Fbetter future for Scotland ` but only
OL,16,FScottish Labour can do that."
OL,26,@nD@KOUtD@AOUxD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/7
