OL,3,CSNP in denial over growing mental
OL,4,Chealth crisis, says Sarwar
OL,6,FClare Haughey, SNP candidate for
OL,7,FRutherglen and Cambuslang, and an NHS
OL,8,Fmental health nurse, said: "Under the
OL,9,FSNP, our NHS has a record number of
OL,10,Fstaff employed to provide mental
OL,11,Fhealth support and our mental health
OL,12,Fbudget for the year exceeds #1.5
OL,13,Fbillion.
OL,15,F"Anas Sarwar and his Labour MSPs
OL,16,Ffailed to back this in Parliament when
OL,17,Fthey had the chance ` and they now
OL,18,Fwant to slash #1 billion from
OL,19,FScotland's NHS which would cut support
OL,20,Ffor people who need it.
OL,26,@pD@\OUwD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777770201
OL,3,CSNP in denial over growing mental
OL,4,Chealth crisis, says Sarwar
OL,6,F"In contrast, a re-elected SNP
OL,7,Fgovernment will expand Scotland's NHS
OL,8,F24 Mental Health Hub to include
OL,9,Fpsychological therapies, and we will
OL,10,Falso invest an additional #3.5 million
OL,11,Fthis year to make it easier for people
OL,12,Fto get the help they need.
OL,14,F"This is the sort of serious action
OL,15,Fyou get from the SNP under John
OL,16,FSwinney's reliable leadership."
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOUxD@_O]
